        "html": "<div class=\"article\" style=\"height: auto !important;\">\n<h1>Section 8 Pays For Your Rental Costs</h1><div id=\"adv3\"></div>\n\n<p>The Housing Choice Vouchers Program, generally known as Section 8, is a federal program that assists seniors, low-income families, and disabled people who cannot afford appropriate and safe housing.</p>\n<img alt=\"Section 8 Pays For Your Rental Costs_1\" class=\"old_img\" src=\"./Public/Images/postImg/section-8-pays-for-your-rental-costs_1.webp\"/>\n</div>",
